data.description: Welcome to this well-maintained single story pool home in Rose Hill Groves. Recently updated with a New Roof in 2022, a Remodeled Master bathroom, an updated kitchen with dark wood cabinets, Granite counters and ALL BRAND-NEW Samsung appliances this year, this home is ready to be enjoyed by its new owners!  Other updates include New A/C end of 2020, new vinyl fence surrounding the entire yard, complete pool rescreening 2022, windows and sliding doors! The home was replumbed this year and also has a new water heater.  With a split floor plan for privacy from the family or guests, the two bedrooms have new carpet and offer a nice separation from the spacious master bedroom on the other side of the house. The kitchen/family area features 18x18 neutral porcelain tile, vaulted ceilings and a cozy space to enjoy the wood burning fireplace while hosting friends and family. Separate dining room and formal living room with bay window provide additional space to entertain company or simply relax. Step out to the pool deck and you will quickly appreciate the large screened and covered area available to enjoy throughout the year! Plenty of space is available to create your ideal outdoor living and leisure space next to the oversized pool with spa!  Conveniently located to major access roads facilitates commute time to downtown Orlando, downtown Winter Garden, area shopping and dining, and theme park visits.
